{"id": "1437177636983017583", "channel_id": "1436325799689982103", "type": 0, "author_id": "198438216628568064", "author_name": "junakaru4ever", "author_bot": false, "content": "让我相信他们有时间把所有限定所有常驻在限定加三维之后的组队情况使用率都完完整整全面测过了再落地，不如信我是秦始皇", "timestamp": "2025-11-09T20:30:50.126000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2025-11-09T20:35:32.046000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "wisdom", "emoji_id": "1400771656510734356", "count": 3}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1436325799689982103", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "V2.4.0 版本前瞻-下┊ Version Outlook - Part Ⅱ", "forum_channel_id": "1355085076500578363", "thread_tags": ["1357267957901951088", "1357267999253467207"]}
{"id": "1437177691693645995", "channel_id": "1436325799689982103", "type": 0, "author_id": "198438216628568064", "author_name": "junakaru4ever", "author_bot": false, "content": "就你游那点人", "timestamp": "2025-11-09T20:31:03.170000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1436325799689982103", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "V2.4.0 版本前瞻-下┊ Version Outlook - Part Ⅱ", "forum_channel_id": "1355085076500578363", "thread_tags": ["1357267957901951088", "1357267999253467207"]}
{"id": "1437178249766768733", "channel_id": "1436325799689982103", "type": 0, "author_id": "198438216628568064", "author_name": "junakaru4ever", "author_bot": false, "content": "星辰篇刚开始限出牌数，后来发现过头了再给一些角色的特定卡加了无视出牌限制来往回找补，刚开始砍毒反上限，这次又加回去", "timestamp": "2025-11-09T20:33:16.225000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2025-11-09T20:34:09.793000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1436325799689982103", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "V2.4.0 版本前瞻-下┊ Version Outlook - Part Ⅱ", "forum_channel_id": "1355085076500578363", "thread_tags": ["1357267957901951088", "1357267999253467207"]}
{"id": "1437178969093967932", "channel_id": "1436325799689982103", "type": 0, "author_id": "198438216628568064", "author_name": "junakaru4ever", "author_bot": false, "content": "<:snicker:1400771784982397049>", "timestamp": "2025-11-09T20:36:07.726000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1436325799689982103", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "V2.4.0 版本前瞻-下┊ Version Outlook - Part Ⅱ", "forum_channel_id": "1355085076500578363", "thread_tags": ["1357267957901951088", "1357267999253467207"]}
{"id": "1437180175530856468", "channel_id": "1436325799689982103", "type": 0, "author_id": "198438216628568064", "author_name": "junakaru4ever", "author_bot": false, "content": "说我个人猜测，我倒不觉得主要是为了逼氪膨胀加，因为加三维属于抽0启就起效了，你游0启能赚啥钱。直接给地瓜鸟弟超限做更强完事了。", "timestamp": "2025-11-09T20:40:55.363000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1436325799689982103", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "V2.4.0 版本前瞻-下┊ Version Outlook - Part Ⅱ", "forum_channel_id": "1355085076500578363", "thread_tags": ["1357267957901951088", "1357267999253467207"]}
{"id": "1437180997098672272", "channel_id": "1436325799689982103", "type": 0, "author_id": "198438216628568064", "author_name": "junakaru4ever", "author_bot": false, "content": "看起来目标像是跟主线降难度配套的拉新+训新人+促销操作，不只是让新人打得更简单，你游更想让新人思想钢印：花钱抽卡池里的限定就能更好打。花钱才好，花钱>研究组队。以前你游入坑是花钱当老板抽最新限定+4，但只要不学配队也不一定打得过，你猫觉得这样妨碍拉新卖卡了想求变。", "timestamp": "2025-11-09T20:44:11.240000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2025-11-09T21:08:57.121000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1436325799689982103", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "V2.4.0 版本前瞻-下┊ Version Outlook - Part Ⅱ", "forum_channel_id": "1355085076500578363", "thread_tags": ["1357267957901951088", "1357267999253467207"]}
{"id": "1437181642522497034", "channel_id": "1436325799689982103", "type": 0, "author_id": "198438216628568064", "author_name": "junakaru4ever", "author_bot": false, "content": "限定天生比常驻高贵是外面其他抽卡二游的常规设置，还有很多干脆搞成常驻都是垃圾的。你猫不想完全放弃你游“常驻限定区别没有那么大，常驻也有加强可以玩”的特色，但又想让新人多来点限定多卖点，所以一边常规加强常驻，表示没有抛弃常驻，一边额外给限定加点数值", "timestamp": "2025-11-09T20:46:45.121000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1436325799689982103", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "V2.4.0 版本前瞻-下┊ Version Outlook - Part Ⅱ", "forum_channel_id": "1355085076500578363", "thread_tags": ["1357267957901951088", "1357267999253467207"]}
{"id": "1437181808922984592", "channel_id": "1436325799689982103", "type": 0, "author_id": "198438216628568064", "author_name": "junakaru4ever", "author_bot": false, "content": "至于效果会怎么样我就不知道了，我猜他们自己都不知道", "timestamp": "2025-11-09T20:47:24.794000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1436325799689982103", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "V2.4.0 版本前瞻-下┊ Version Outlook - Part Ⅱ", "forum_channel_id": "1355085076500578363", "thread_tags": ["1357267957901951088", "1357267999253467207"]}
{"id": "1437182315423076362", "channel_id": "1436325799689982103", "type": 0, "author_id": "198438216628568064", "author_name": "junakaru4ever", "author_bot": false, "content": "他也怕玩崩，这暗搓搓拉通加一点基础数值，然后装死就是试探呗", "timestamp": "2025-11-09T20:49:25.553000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1436325799689982103", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "V2.4.0 版本前瞻-下┊ Version Outlook - Part Ⅱ", "forum_channel_id": "1355085076500578363", "thread_tags": ["1357267957901951088", "1357267999253467207"]}
{"id": "1437183270604243016", "channel_id": "1436325799689982103", "type": 0, "author_id": "198438216628568064", "author_name": "junakaru4ever", "author_bot": false, "content": "倒也不觉得之后怪物会变得更难，水温会立马上升。因为上面说了，我觉得这波限定加数值是为了照顾新入坑抽了0命新卡的新老板让他们玩得更爽，结合周年降主线难度为了弱保软，马上升温还怎么哄新老板。况且洋人那边平均游戏水平和理解比中文区差远了，你游现在提升一点水温洋人都得跑", "timestamp": "2025-11-09T20:53:13.286000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1436325799689982103", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "V2.4.0 版本前瞻-下┊ Version Outlook - Part Ⅱ", "forum_channel_id": "1355085076500578363", "thread_tags": ["1357267957901951088", "1357267999253467207"]}
{"id": "1437183951541370880", "channel_id": "1436325799689982103", "type": 0, "author_id": "198438216628568064", "author_name": "junakaru4ever", "author_bot": false, "content": "但是这操作对一路支持游戏的老玩家尤其是常驻角色厨就寒心了。因为第一次把种姓制摆台面上了。二游的魂是角色厨力，牢猫你游对比第九史诗最大优势其实就是你游还有角色厨ip粉，那边没有。你不要伤人家的心。角色厨ip粉比起单纯蝗虫只看数值的玩家，更有粘性，更愿意长青付费，更愿意包容你的问题，你应该知道", "timestamp": "2025-11-09T20:55:55.634000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2025-11-09T21:18:12.446000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "☝️", "emoji_id": null, "count": 5}, {"emoji": "agree", "emoji_id": "1400771815076528258", "count": 5}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1436325799689982103", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "V2.4.0 版本前瞻-下┊ Version Outlook - Part Ⅱ", "forum_channel_id": "1355085076500578363", "thread_tags": ["1357267957901951088", "1357267999253467207"]}
{"id": "1437185443413233858", "channel_id": "1436325799689982103", "type": 0, "author_id": "198438216628568064", "author_name": "junakaru4ever", "author_bot": false, "content": "fgo也摆明了数值种姓制，五星卡默认最高90级，四星80，三星70。 但是fgo可以低星厨喂圣杯，喂上去大家都可以120级。你游现在实际上就是从大家都默认最高60，改成限定默认最高70了。你如果实在要在这方面学fgo，可以，那你至少也得允许常驻卡可以喂更多的等级突破道具，多喂10级，和限定卡平齐，至少我不会觉得我推常驻卡永远矮一截，别只学一半", "timestamp": "2025-11-09T21:01:51.324000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "☝️", "emoji_id": null, "count": 7}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1436325799689982103", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "V2.4.0 版本前瞻-下┊ Version Outlook - Part Ⅱ", "forum_channel_id": "1355085076500578363", "thread_tags": ["1357267957901951088", "1357267999253467207"]}
{"id": "1437186161436266710", "channel_id": "1436325799689982103", "type": 0, "author_id": "198438216628568064", "author_name": "junakaru4ever", "author_bot": false, "content": "而且我不拉踩，但你游实际上就是常驻池很多卡颜值厨力都比最新的星辰篇限定高啊，不像别的游戏限定都是最好看的人气最高的，你游还真不一定限定比常驻好看。很多最美的还是老卡。牢猫别小看常驻的人气，与其跟常驻厨子对着干，不如合作，你出的新墨菲如果能带飞深海老常驻怕没人抽吗", "timestamp": "2025-11-09T21:04:42.514000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2025-11-09T21:05:17.688000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "👆", "emoji_id": null, "count": 7}, {"emoji": "agree", "emoji_id": "1400771815076528258", "count": 4}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1436325799689982103", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "V2.4.0 版本前瞻-下┊ Version Outlook - Part Ⅱ", "forum_channel_id": "1355085076500578363", "thread_tags": ["1357267957901951088", "1357267999253467207"]}
